   Pwogram achte kle nan men\n                                                    <\/a>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n\n                                                \n                                                <div class=\"vip-mega-panel vip-mega-card\">\n                                                                                                        <a class=\"vip-mega-link\"\n                                                        href=\"\/ht\/ipotek\/pre-ipotek\">\n                                                        Pr\u00e8 ipot\u00e8k\n                                                    <\/a>\n                                                                                                    <\/div>\n                                            <\/div>\n\n                                        <\/div>\n                                                                            <\/div>\n                                <\/div>\n\n                            <\/div>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/li>\n\n                <!-- Liens normaux -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/ht\/construction\">Ekip Nou an<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/ht\/carrieres\">Kary\u00e8<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/ht\/partenaires\">Patn\u00e8 yo<\/a><\/li>\n                <li class=\"nav-item\"><a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/ht\/contact\">Kontak<\/a><\/li>\n\n                <!-- CTA -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item ms-xl-2 my-3 my-xl-0\">\n                    <a href=\"\/ht\/contact\" class=\"btn vip-btn-gold rounded-pill px-4 py-2 w-100 w-xl-auto\">\n                        Konsiltasyon Gratis\n                    <\/a>\n                <\/li>\n\n                <!-- Mobile: lien Services simple -->\n                <li class=\"nav-item d-xl-none\">\n                    <a class=\"nav-link\" href=\"\/ht\/services\">S\u00e8vis yo<\/a>\n                <\/li>\n\n            <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/nav>\r\n    \r\n    \n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-white\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-7\">\n                <h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-4 text-primary\">Kisa Asirans maladi grav la ye nan Keb\u00e8k?<\/h2>\n                <p class=\"lead text-muted\">Asirans maladi grav la se yon pwoteksyon finansye ki peye yon s\u00f2m lajan yon s\u00e8l kou ki pa enpozab l\u00e8 yon moun ki asire resevwa dyagnostik yon maladi grav ki kouvri nan kontra li a. Ou ka s\u00e8vi ak k\u00f2b sa a jan w vle, san w pa bezwen bay pr\u00e8v, pou w ka f\u00e8 fas ak konsekans finansye maladi a pote.<\/p>\n                <h4 class=\"fw-bold mt-5 mb-3\">Maladi ki kouvri yo<\/h4>\n                <p>Sa pral depann de konpayi asirans lan, yon kontra ka kouvri ant 4 ak 30 maladi grav, tankou:<\/p>\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                                        <div class=\"col-md-6 mb-2\">\n                        <div class=\"d-flex align-items-center\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-check text-warning me-2\"><\/i>\n                            <span>Kans\u00e8<\/span>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                        <div class=\"col-md-6 mb-2\">\n                        <div class=\"d-flex align-items-center\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-check text-warning me-2\"><\/i>\n                            <span>Aksidan vaskil\u00e8 serebral (Konjesyon serebral \/ AVC)<\/span>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                        <div class=\"col-md-6 mb-2\">\n                        <div class=\"d-flex align-items-center\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-check text-warning me-2\"><\/i>\n                            <span>Enfaktis myokad (Kriz kadyak)<\/span>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                        <div class=\"col-md-6 mb-2\">\n                        <div class=\"d-flex align-items-center\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-check text-warning me-2\"><\/i>\n                            <span>Skeleroz an plak<\/span>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                        <div class=\"col-md-6 mb-2\">\n                        <div class=\"d-flex align-items-center\">\n                            <i class=\"fas fa-check text-warning me-2\"><\/i>\n                            <span>L\u00f2t gwo maladi<\/span>\n                        <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n                                    <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-5 text-center mt-4 mt-lg-0\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceMaladieGrave\/A-cote-texte-Maladies-Graves.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid rounded-4 shadow\"\n                    alt=\"Maladies Graves\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-light\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row g-5 align-items-center flex-lg-row-reverse\">\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <h2 class=\"fw-bold mb-4\">Asirans maladi grav ak RAMQ : ki diferans ki genyen?<\/h2>\n                <p>Nan Keb\u00e8k, RAMQ kouvri swen medikal debaz yo (konsiltasyon, ent\u00e8ne lopital, zak medikal).<\/p>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-4 shadow-sm border-start border-4 border-danger\">\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold text-danger mb-3\">Poutan, RAMQ pa kouvri:<\/h5>\n                    <ul class=\"list-unstyled mb-0\">\n                                                <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-times-circle text-danger me-2\"><\/i> Lajan ou p\u00e8di paske w pa ka travay<\/li>\n                                                <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-times-circle text-danger me-2\"><\/i> Medikaman ki pa asire yo<\/li>\n                                                <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-times-circle text-danger me-2\"><\/i> Tretman prive oswa tretman rapid<\/li>\n                                                <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-times-circle text-danger me-2\"><\/i> Swen nan kay<\/li>\n                                                <li class=\"mb-2\"><i class=\"fas fa-times-circle text-danger me-2\"><\/i> Deplasman, aranjman nan kay la oswa depans p\u00e8son\u00e8l<\/li>\n                                            <\/ul>\n                <\/div>\n                <p class=\"mt-4 fst-italic text-muted\">Asirans maladi grav la vin konplete RAMQ, li pwoteje estabilite finansye moun ki asire a ansanm ak fanmi l l\u00e8 gen yon gwo dyagnostik.<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n                <img src=\"https:\/\/vipgpi.net\/assets\/img\/assuranceMaladieGrave\/AdobeStock_727436851.jpg\" class=\"img-fluid rounded-4 shadow\"\n                    alt=\"RAMQ vs Private\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-white\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-center fw-bold mb-2\">Konsekans finansye rey\u00e8l yon maladi grav pote<\/h2>\n        <p class=\"text-center text-muted mb-5\">Dyagnostik yon maladi grav bay anpil estr\u00e8s finansye ki ka dire pandan plizy\u00e8 ane. Men gwo konsekans yo :<\/p>\n        <div class=\"row g-4\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 bg-light p-4 rounded-4 shadow-sm\">\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold text-primary mb-3\">1. P\u00e8t revni<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Moun p\u00e8di an mway\u00e8n $20 000 l\u00e8 yo sispann travay pout\u00e8t maladi oswa tretman. Moun k ap bay swen yo (edan) p\u00e8di an mway\u00e8n 25 % nan revni yo tou.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 bg-light p-4 rounded-4 shadow-sm\">\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold text-primary mb-3\">2. Depans dir\u00e8k pou lavi<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Pri total yon kans\u00e8 pou yon pasyan mwayen nan Kanada evalye a pr\u00e8ske $33 000. Nan lane 2024, yo estime depans pasyan yo ak fanmi yo f\u00e8 rive nan 5,2 milya dola.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 bg-light p-4 rounded-4 shadow-sm\">\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold text-primary mb-3\">3. Tretman ak medikaman<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Pri mway\u00e8n pou yon seri tretman se $65 000 pou nouvo medikaman yo. Menm l\u00e8 w asire, ou ka oblije peye jiska 20 % nan fr\u00e8 yo.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\n                <div class=\"card h-100 border-0 bg-light p-4 rounded-4 shadow-sm\">\n                    <h5 class=\"fw-bold text-primary mb-3\">4. L\u00f2t fr\u00e8 endir\u00e8k<\/h5>\n                    <p class=\"small text-muted mb-0\">Depans k ap anpile vit : deplasman, pakin, manje nan lopital, kote pou d\u00f2mi, moun pou gade timoun, netwayaj kay, pwot\u00e8z ak matery\u00e8l medikal.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n        <div class=\"mt-5 p-4 bg-warning bg-opacity-10 border-start border-4 border-warning rounded text-center\">\n            <p class=\"mb-0 fw-bold text-dark\"><i class=\"fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2\"><\/i>\n                Dapre yon etid, 44 % pasyan oblije pran nan ekonomi yo, 27 % oblije prete lajan epi 26 % tounen al travay anvan menm yo geri n\u00e8t.\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-dark text-white\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-center fw-bold mb-5\">\u00c8ske w te konnen?<\/h2>\n        <div class=\"row g-4\">\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div class=\"d-flex mb-4\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line text-warning fa-2x me-3\"><\/i>\n                    <p class=\"mb-0\">Pr\u00e8ske 1 sou 2 moun ap f\u00e8 kans\u00e8 pandan lavi yo, epi 1 sou 4 ap mouri anba l.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div class=\"d-flex mb-4\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line text-warning fa-2x me-3\"><\/i>\n                    <p class=\"mb-0\">Nan Kanada, yo estime ap gen anviwon 0,48 dyagnostik chak minit nan lane 2025.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div class=\"d-flex mb-4\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line text-warning fa-2x me-3\"><\/i>\n                    <p class=\"mb-0\">Yo dyagnostike 1 moun sou 4 ak yon maladi kadyak nan Kanada.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div class=\"d-flex mb-4\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line text-warning fa-2x me-3\"><\/i>\n                    <p class=\"mb-0\">90 % Kanadyen panse yon dyagnostik konsa t ap gen yon gwo enpak sou finans yo.<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n                    <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/section>\n\n\n<section class=\"section-padding bg-light\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-center fw-bold mb-5\">Kesyon moun poze pi souvan (FAQ)<\/h2>\n        <div class